metadata.description: Tiny Kills "Killer Werewolves", much like Killer Dolls, are also a drop for Tiny Kills Genesis holders, with one exception - a portion of Killer Werewolves are also available for mint!  1,313 were reserved for Genesis Killer holders, with an overall max supply after mint of 6,666!  Each are collectible and tradable on OpenSea and the Ethereum blockchain, and feature a variety of weapons, clothing items, backgrounds, effects, and more!  Note - once a Genesis Killer Werewolf claim is claimed, the claim is forever consumed!
metadata.name: Wolf #2
